    dc:description "Fig. 3. Male diagnostic features of Labomimus cucphuong sp. nov.A – right antennal club, in ventral view; B – pronotum; C – metaventral process, lateral view; D – protrochanter and profemur; E – apex of protibia; F – mesotrochanter and mesofemur; G – metatrochanter and metafemur; H–J – aedeagus, in dorsal (H), lateral (I), and ventral (J) view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm in A, B, D, F, G; 0.2 mm in C, H, I, J; 0.05 mm in E." ;
